Uses of Package
com.siemens.icm.io

Packages that use com.siemens.icm.io
com.siemens.icm.io Siemens IMP utility classes for accessing the functionality of a wireless module.  
 

Classes in com.siemens.icm.io used by com.siemens.icm.io
ATCommandFailedException
          Signals that a requested device access via the ATCommand class failed.
ATCommandListener
          The ATCommandListener interface defines the capabilities for receiving unsolicited AT-Events (e.g. like "RING") and changes of the relevant incoming interface signals (RING, DCD and DSR).
ATCommandResponseListener
          The ATCommandResponseListenerListener interface defines the capabilities for receiving the response of sending an AT command to a module's AT interpreter.
